      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bindings in which the back of a text block is trimmed to produce a block of separate leaves, an adhesive is applied to the area, and the cover is affixed.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
